@node Purpose
@subsection Purpose

Establish the working relationship, boundaries, and rhythm before any technical work
begins. Everything in Phase 1 is harder if you skip this.

@node Checklist
@subsection Checklist

@itemize
@item
Create @samp{clients/<client>/CONTEXT.md} (domain vocabulary, key people, tech stack)
@item
Create system discovery master doc (@samp{C-c c ed} for sessions; master doc manually)
@item
